GitHubApiData.name: iCellR
GitHubApiData.description: iCellR is an interactive R package designed to facilitate the analysis and visualization of high-throughput single-cell sequencing data. It supports a variety of single-cell technologies, including scRNA-seq, scVDJ-seq, scATAC-seq, CITE-Seq, and Spatial Transcriptomics (ST).

TranslatedDescriptions.ja: iCellRは、高スループット単一細胞シーケンシングデータの解析と可視化を支援するインタラクティブなRパッケージです。scRNA-seq、scVDJ-seq、scATAC-seq、CITE-Seq、Spatial Transcriptomics（ST）など、さまざまな単一細胞技術に対応しています。
TranslatedDescriptions.zh-CN: iCellR 是一个交互式 R 包，旨在简化高通量单细胞测序数据的分析与可视化。它支持多种单细胞技术，包括 scRNA-seq、scVDJ-seq、scATAC-seq、CITE-Seq 和空间转录组学（ST）。
TranslatedDescriptions.en: iCellR is an interactive R package designed to facilitate the analysis and visualization of high-throughput single-cell sequencing data. It supports various single-cell technologies, including scRNA-seq, scVDJ-seq, scATAC-seq, CITE-Seq, and Spatial Transcriptomics (ST).
TranslatedDescriptions.ko: iCellR은 고처리량 단일 세포 시퀀싱 데이터의 분석 및 시각화를 용이하게 하는 인터랙티브 R 패키지입니다. scRNA-seq, scVDJ-seq, scATAC-seq, CITE-Seq, 공간 전사체학(ST) 등 다양한 단일 세포 기술을 지원합니다.
TranslatedDescriptions.fr: iCellR est un package R interactif conçu pour faciliter l'analyse et la visualisation des données de séquençage unicellulaire à haut débit. Il prend en charge diverses technologies unicellulaires, notamment scRNA-seq, scVDJ-seq, scATAC-seq, CITE-Seq et la transcriptomique spatiale (ST).
TranslatedDescriptions.es: iCellR es un paquete interactivo de R diseñado para facilitar el análisis y la visualización de datos de secuenciación unicelular de alto rendimiento. Soporta diversas tecnologías unicelulares, incluyendo scRNA-seq, scVDJ-seq, scATAC-seq, CITE-Seq y Transcriptómica Espacial (ST).
